{
  "stem": "4226.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the roof was one over the whole lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the goods arriving there were very bulky stuff-- sugar, and rice, and flour, and some goodies, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But these were mainly in 50 kilo or-- or larger bags.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to take them up, we had a crane with a steel rope, and then a little electric hoist operated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the truck, truck moved in--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had to move it up through a shaft into the roof section.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And inside the roof, we had trolleys, because different material were in different places.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you couldn't move the trolley from one house to the next because of these two-foot brick walls.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you had to take another trolley and repack them maybe two or three times.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some goods were on the same place, which we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course the-- the manager told us you can eat cheese, sardines, anything open.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But don't take anything into the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we-- we had even wafers there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Military stuff.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Lunch-- lunch hour, we-- we got-- we got 16 liters sent out from the camp, hot food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we didn't even touch it while we here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We-- we didn't want to take it back to the camp, so they wouldn't find out that we eat all the goodies.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We throw them in the rubbish, on the gutter down, the 16 liter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We took back the empty, that was insulated like a thermos, for 20 liter ones.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the work was real heavy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We-- we could-- we were there about 10 days, two weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then they canceled us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were weak-- too weak.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They wanted stronger men.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they took stronger ones with guards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we ran back to other groups.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rotschweig.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "R-O-T-H-S-- no, sorry, R-O-T-S-C-H-W-E-I-G.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rotschweig.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
